                "GEMUC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Ionization chamber for fission, Geiger",
                "counter for beta activities."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The capture cross sections were using Y+Be",
                "source and detecting the beta radioactivity formed in",
                "the sample irradiated. The yttrium source cube was",
                "put in contact with an enriched sample of known 235U",
                "content and fission produced were measured in",
                "ionization chamber with a linear amplifier. In this",
                "way, knowing the cross section of 235U, one can",
                "calculate the neutron flux through a sample having a",
                "geometry of the 235U sample."
              ]
            }
          ],
